    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082990/extras/f7f215ad3f99404988bc8aeffcfcaae1.poster.avif?t=1741943615\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082990/extras/f7f215ad3f99404988bc8aeffcfcaae1.webm?t=1741943615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082990/extras/f7f215ad3f99404988bc8aeffcfcaae1.mp4?t=1741943615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1副扑克牌组，19个扑克牌型，172张功能卡牌，21个加强效果，39个反派，2种玩法机制，灵活多样的策略组合，无尽的可能性！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-小丑冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多个反派的减益叠加生效，并拥有暗黑牌组，抵消玩家出牌效果，更具策略和挑战性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-杰克&amp;小丑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将扑克牌型、小丑牌的策略与经典 yatzy结合，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抽牌和锁定扑克牌，匹配目标牌型以击败反派。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-PvP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在【小丑冒险】中保存你满意的种子，与好友或陌生人决斗并赢取奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-能力牌组</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级能力牌组，让你携带更多的资源，获取强大的特殊能力，并解锁部分小丑牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-卡牌</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >120张拥有独特能力的小丑牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >22张可加强扑克牌的塔罗牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18张加强手牌和小丑牌的法术牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12张升级牌型1-3级的星座牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-加强</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5个赋能和7个符印为扑克牌和小丑牌带来加成效果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12个增益在【小丑冒险】中提供特殊能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规则简单，轻松上手，但易学难精，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的元素和可能性，等待你的发现！</p>",
